import { Stack } from "@mui/material"
import { VersionToggle } from "../Atoms"
import EmptyCave from "../Atoms/EmptyCave"
import { useVersionState, versionOptions } from "../Atoms/VersionToggle"

const HomePage = () => {
    const versionState = useVersionState(versionOptions.example)
    return <Stack justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" sx={{ marginBottom: 1080 }}>
        <VersionToggle versionState={versionState} />
        <EmptyCave version={versionState.version} />
    </Stack>
}

export default HomePage
